de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.database.ids

Interface DoubleDBIDList

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DBIDs
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IntegerDBIDKNNList, KNNList, ModifiableDoubleDBIDList
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DoubleIntegerDBIDKNNList, DoubleIntegerDBIDList, DoubleIntegerDBIDListKNNHeap, DoubleIntegerDBIDPairKNNListHeap, DoubleIntegerDBIDPairList, IntegerDBIDKNNSubList, KNNSubList

    public interface DoubleDBIDList
extends DBIDs
    Collection of double values associated with objects. To iterate over the results, use the following code: 
     for (DoubleDBIDListIter iter = result.iter(); iter.valid(); iter.advance()) {
   // You can get the distance via: iter.doubleValue();
   // And use iter just like any other DBIDRef
 }
    If you are only interested in the IDs of the objects, the following is also sufficient: 
     for (DBIDIter iter = result.iter(); iter.valid(); iter.advance()) {
   // Use iter just like any other DBIDRef
 }
    Since:
    0.5.5
    Author:
    Erich Schubert
